# Comprehensive Implementation Plan: "Ask AI" Product Search Feature

## Executive Summary

This plan designs a semantic product search feature using OpenAI embeddings, in-memory vector search, and cosine similarity. The implementation follows the established NestJS patterns in this codebase for REST endpoints, CLI commands, database operations, and service architecture.

## 1. Module Structure

### New Module Location
```
/src/modules/rest/semantic-search/
├── semantic-search.controller.ts
├── semantic-search.service.ts
├── semantic-search.module.ts
└── vector-search.service.ts       # Core vector operations

/src/modules/db/product-embeddings/
├── models/
│   └── product-embedding.model.ts
├── dto/
│   ├── product-embedding.base.dto.ts
│   ├── product-embedding.create.dto.ts
│   └── product-embedding.update.dto.ts
├── types/
│   ├── product-embedding.base.interface.ts
│   ├── product-embedding.create.interface.ts
│   └── product-embedding.update.interface.ts
├── product-embeddings.service.ts
└── product-embeddings.module.ts

/src/dto/semantic-search/
